data.title: JAMES GARRICK, MD
data.meta_description:
8 reviews of JAMES GARRICK, MD "Typical.
"oooo I hurt....make it stop...NOW!!...waah waaah."
Jim Garrick is one of, if not THE most talented and effective physician/surgeons I have known in my life.
It is sad in this culture people expect miracles and blame their doctors if there is not immediate resolution of their symptoms.
Believe me, you will find a surgeon ready and willing to cut you open on a moment's notice when a conservative approach will have a better longterm outcome. Go ahead... go find your butcher and you will regret it the rest of your life.
For now you should follow his advice.

Karlton says, break a leg."
data.text: Claim your business to immediately update business information, respond to reviews, and more!
